Places in the Realms where pickles were known to be produced included:
* The city of [[Myrinjar]] was well known for producing a variety of pickled vegetables.{{Cite polyhedron/135/Elminster's Everwinking Eye: A Wayfarers Guide to the Forgotten Realms|8}}
* In the town of [[Red Larch]], [[Mhandyvver's Poultry]] was known to both produce and sell pickled [[chicken]] liver and eggs. Other farmers in this town were known to produce pickled beets and the [[half-orc]] [[Grund]] operated pickle vats at the market.
* Pickling was a common practice in the nation of [[Turmish]].<ref>{{Cite polyhedron/101/Elminster's Everwinking Eye: Turmish Customers and Festivals|22}}
* In the city of [[Waterdeep]], there was a factory devoted to the production of pickles.{{Cite dragon/425/Spin a Yarn: The Night Thelva Clovenaxe Flew|50}}
* Spicy pickles were considered a comfort peasant food in the village of [[Eveningstar]] in [[Cormyr]].

